description: Professional architectural blueprint for a 1200 Square Feet house with This 3BHK floor plan is designed for a 1,200 sq. ft. plot in New Delhi, Delhi, with a budget of INR 20 lakhs. The layout includes a spacious living room, a dining area, a modular kitchen, three well-ventilated bedrooms, and two modern bathrooms. One bedroom comes with an attached bath, ideal as a master suite. The design maximizes natural light and ventilation, ensuring comfort in the urban climate. A compact front porch and parking space are included. The plan focuses on efficient space utilization, catering to a modern family's needs within a cost-effective and practical construction approach.. Top-down 2D floor plan with precise measurements, clean lines, labeled rooms, doors, windows, and dimensions. Technical architectural drawing style with blue lines on white background.
